      <div class="chart-wrap" style="height:280px">
        <canvas id="c_qcpth1" role="img" aria-label="Pareto chart QCPTH1. Top: Misinserted 572 (54.12%).">QCPTH1 defects: Misinserted 572, Insuff solder 206, Missing 164, No lead protrusion 43, Excess solder 34, Damaged 18, Wrong Part 13, Others 7.</canvas>
      </div>
